title: Undefeated Spring 2017 Is Filled With Sportswear Favorites
text:
Visit the original post to see all 19 images from this gallery. 
Brand: Undefeated
Season: Spring 2017
Key Pieces: Tracksuits, soccer jerseys, basketball tops and bottoms.
Editor’s Notes: Undefeated’s new spring selection finds the streetwear brand sticking to its familiar sports aesthetic. The collection becomes available this Friday, February 24, at all Undefeated chapter stores and online .
For more fashion news, check out Stone Island Shadow Project’s new SS17 array that is all about technical bangers.
